\begin_layout Subsection
QCD拉氏量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
QCD 是强相互作用的规范理论，颜色 SU(3) 作为它底层的规范群。历史上，为了解释三夸克态–重子的 Pauli 不相容原理，引入了颜色自由度。QCD
 的物质场被称为夸克，它们是自旋 
\begin_inset Formula $1/2$
\end_inset

 的费米子，有六种味道
\begin_inset Formula $\left(u,d,s,c,b,t\right)$
\end_inset

，在三种颜色之外。由于还没有观测到渐近自由态的夸克，夸克质量的意义和数值都跟从重子性质中提取的方法密切相关。对于轻夸克的流夸克质量，应该把它们仅仅看成对称性破缺
的参数，它们的大小提供了手征对称性破缺的程度。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在 color 规范变换下，各种场对象的变换方式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
q_{f}(x)\mapsto q_{f}^{\prime}(x)=\exp\left(-i\Theta_{a}(x)\frac{\lambda_{a}^{c}}{2}\right)q_{f}(x)\equiv U(x)q_{f}(x)
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

是颜色指标，
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{a}^{c}$
\end_inset

是 Gell-Mann 矩阵。夸克场按照基础表示变换。adjoint quark field, 伴随夸克场 按照
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & q_{f}(x)\mapsto\exp\left(-i\Theta_{a}\left(x\right)\frac{\lambda_{a}^{c}}{2}\right)q_{f}\left(x\right)\equiv U(x)q_{f}(x)\\
 & q_{f}^{\dagger}(x)\mapsto q_{f}^{\dagger}(x)U^{\dagger}(x)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

规范场变换为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{A}_{\mu}\equiv\mathcal{A}_{a\mu}\frac{\lambda_{a}^{c}}{2}\mapsto\mathcal{A}_{\mu}^{\prime}=U\mathcal{A}_{\mu}U^{\dagger}-\frac{i}{g}U\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}
\]

\end_inset

协变导数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{\mu}q_{f}=\left(\partial_{\mu}+ig\mathcal{A}_{\mu}\right)q_{f}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

是耦合常数。规范场的动力学需要：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\mathcal{F}_{a,\mu\nu} & \equiv\partial_{\mu}\mathcal{A}_{a\nu}-\partial_{\nu}\mathcal{A}_{a\mu}-gf_{abc}\mathcal{A}_{b\mu}\mathcal{A}_{c\nu}\nonumber \\
\mathcal{F}_{\mu\nu} & \equiv\partial_{\mu}\mathcal{A}_{\nu}-\partial_{\nu}\mathcal{A}_{\mu}+ig\left[\mathcal{A}_{\mu},\mathcal{A}_{\nu}\right]\nonumber \\
\mathcal{F}_{\mu\nu} & \equiv\mathcal{F}_{a,\mu\nu}\frac{\lambda_{a}^{c}}{2}\mapsto U\mathcal{F}_{\mu\nu}U^{\dagger}\label{eq:1.27}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \partial_{\mu}\left(U\mathcal{A}_{\nu}U^{\dagger}-\frac{i}{g}U\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right)-\partial_{\nu}\left(U\mathcal{A}_{\mu}U^{\dagger}-\frac{i}{g}U\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)+ig\left[U\mathcal{A}_{\mu}U^{\dagger}-\frac{i}{g}U\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger},U\mathcal{A}_{\nu}U^{\dagger}-\frac{i}{g}U\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right]\\
 & {\color{lime}{\color{cyan}U\partial_{\mu}\mathcal{A}_{\nu}U^{\dagger}-U\partial_{\nu}\mathcal{A}_{\mu}U^{\dagger}+igU\left[\mathcal{A}_{\mu},\mathcal{A}_{\nu}\right]U^{\dagger}}}\\
 & +{\color{blue}\left(\partial_{\mu}U\right)\mathcal{A}_{\nu}U^{\dagger}-\left(\partial_{\nu}U\right)\mathcal{A}_{\mu}U^{\dagger}+U\mathcal{A}_{\nu}\left(\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)-U\mathcal{A}_{\mu}\left(\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right)}\\
 & {\color{red}-\frac{i}{g}\left(\partial_{\mu}\left(U\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right)-\partial_{\nu}\left(U\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)\right)}\\
 & {\color{red}=-\frac{i}{g}\left(\left(\partial_{\mu}U\right)\left(\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right)-\left(\partial_{\nu}U\right)\left(\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)+U\partial_{\mu}\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}-U\partial_{\nu}\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)=0}\\
\\
 & {\color{blue}+\left[U\mathcal{A}_{\mu}U^{\dagger},U\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right]+\left[U\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger},U\mathcal{A}_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right]={\color{blue}UA_{\mu}\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}-UA_{\nu}\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}+\partial_{\nu}UA_{\mu}U^{\dagger}-\partial_{\mu}UA_{\nu}U^{\dagger}}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

注意，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\partial_{\mu}U\right)\left(\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger}\right)-\left(\partial_{\nu}U\right)\left(\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)=\partial_{\mu}k\partial_{\nu}k-\partial_{\nu}k\partial_{\mu}k=0,U=\exp\left(\mathbbm{1}+k\right)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\lambda_{a}^{c}}{2}$
\end_inset

上分量和矩阵形式可以通过正交关系联系起来：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\tr\left(\lambda_{a}\lambda_{b}\right)=2\delta_{ab}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\tr\left(\lambda_{a}\right)=0
\end{equation}

\end_inset

QCD 拉氏量为:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}_{\text{QCD}}^{0}=\sum_{l=u,d,s,c,b,t}\bar{q}_{f}\left(i\slashed{D}-m_{f}\right)q_{f}-\frac{1}{4}\mathcal{F}_{a\mu\nu}\mathcal{F}^{a\mu\nu}
\]

\end_inset

使用
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.4"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\tr\left(\lambda_{a}\lambda_{b}\right)=2\delta_{ab}$
\end_inset

，胶子部分可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{1}{2}\tr_{c}\left(\mathcal{F}_{\mu\nu}\mathcal{F}^{\mu\nu}\right)
\]

\end_inset

然后使用求迹的轮换对称性，
\begin_inset Formula $\tr\left(AB\right)=\tr\left(BA\right)$
\end_inset

，以及
\begin_inset Formula $UU^{\dagger}=\mathbbm{1}$
\end_inset

，容易看出它在
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.27"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

下是不变的。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
q_{L} & \mapsto U_{L}q_{L}=\exp\left(-i\Theta_{L}\right)\exp\left(-i\sum_{a=1}^{8}\Theta_{La}\frac{\lambda_{a}}{2}\right)q_{L}\\
q_{R} & \mapsto U_{R}q_{R}=\exp\left(-i\Theta_{R}\right)\exp\left(-i\sum_{a=1}^{8}\Theta_{Ra}\frac{\lambda_{a}}{2}\right)q_{R}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

 是独立的变换。提取出 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp\left(-i\Theta_{L}\right)$
\end_inset

 是为了方便。一个对角的
\begin_inset Formula $U(1)$
\end_inset

变换，总可以提取出 迹不为零的部分，和迹为零的部分，后者可以分解到 SU(3) Gell-man 矩阵中。总共有
\begin_inset Formula $2*(8+1)=19$
\end_inset

