\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.114"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的拉氏量，或者
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.132"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的哈密顿量决定。包含
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi^{\dagger},\Phi$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $J^{\mu}$
\end_inset

的格林函数可以通过对
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.130"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

求泛函偏导得到，比如，
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.127"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

中的格林函数由下式给出，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
G^{\mu}\left(x,y,z\right)=\left.\left(-i\right)^{3}\frac{\delta^{3}Z\left[j,j^{*},j^{\mu}\right]}{\delta j^{*}\left(x\right)\delta j_{\mu}\left(y\right)\delta j\left(z\right)}\right|_{j=0,j^{*}=0,j_{\mu}=0}\label{eq:1.134}
\end{equation}

