\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Z\left[j,j^{*},j^{\mu}\right]=\langle0,\text{out}|0,\text{in}\rangle_{j,j^{*},j_{\mu}}
\]

\end_inset

为了讨论理论底层的对称性对生成泛函施加的限制，我们考虑它的路径积分表示
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Z\left[j,j^{*},j^{\mu}\right]=\int\left[\dif\Phi_{1}\right]\left[\dif\Phi_{2}\right]\exp\left[iS\left[\Phi,\Phi^{*},j,j^{*},j_{\mu}\right]\right]
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
S\left[\Phi,\Phi^{*},j,j^{*},j_{\mu}\right]=S\left[\Phi,\Phi^{*}\right]+\int\dif^{4}x\left[\Phi\left(x\right)j^{*}\left(x\right)+\Phi^{*}\left(x\right)j\left(x\right)+J^{\mu}\left(x\right)j_{\mu}\left(x\right)\right]\label{eq:1.137}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

作用量加上外源耦合项。在路径积分表示中，我们处理泛函积分，来代替处理线性算符。下面我们用
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi^{*}$
\end_inset

来代替
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

。我们考虑场的定域无穷小变换，并同时要求外源也变换
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
j^{\prime}\left(x\right)=\left[1+i\varepsilon\left(x\right)\right]j\left(x\right),\quad j^{\prime*}\left(x\right)=\left[1-i\varepsilon\left(x\right)\right]j^{*}\left(x\right),\quad j_{\mu}^{\prime}\left(x\right)=j_{\mu}\left(x\right)-\partial_{\mu}\left(x\right)\label{eq:1.138}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.137"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

在这样的定域变换下不变
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S\left[\Phi^{\prime},\Phi^{\prime*},j^{\prime},j^{\prime*},j_{\mu}^{\prime}\right]=S\left[\Phi,\Phi^{*},j,j^{*},j_{\mu}\right]
\]

\end_inset

我们强调外源
\begin_inset Formula $j_{\mu}$
\end_inset

的变换是必要的，用来抵消 Lagrangian 动能项的变化。另外注意 Lagrangian 的 global 对称性决定了
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.138"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

中的具体变换形式。我们如下可以验证生成泛函的不变性，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
Z\left[j,j^{*},j_{\mu}\right] & =\int\left[\dif\Phi_{1}\right]\left[\dif\Phi_{2}\right]e^{iS\left[\Phi,\Phi^{*},j,j^{*},j_{\mu}\right]}\nonumber \\
 & =\int\left[\dif\Phi_{1}\right]\left[\dif\Phi_{2}\right]e^{iS\left[\Phi^{\prime},\Phi^{\prime*},j^{\prime},j^{\prime*},j_{\mu}^{\prime}\right]}\nonumber \\
 & =\int\left[\dif\Phi_{1}^{\prime}\right]\left[\dif\Phi_{2}^{\prime}\right]\left(\frac{\partial\Phi_{i}}{\partial\Phi_{j}^{\prime}}\right)e^{iS\left[\Phi^{\prime},\Phi^{\prime*},j^{\prime},j^{\prime*},j_{\mu}^{\prime}\right]}\label{eq:1.140}\\
 & =\int\left[\dif\Phi_{1}\right]\left[\dif\Phi_{2}\right]e^{iS\left[\Phi,\Phi^{*},j^{\prime},j^{\prime*},j_{\mu}^{\prime}\right]}\nonumber \\
 & =Z\left[j^{\prime},j^{\prime*},j_{\mu}^{\prime}\right]\nonumber 
\end{align}

\end_inset

我们使用了 Jacobi 行列式等于
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

以及重命名积分变量。换句话说，如果
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1.114"
