-Q_{2}\\
Q_{1}\\
Q_{3}
\end{array}\right)=\exp\left(i\frac{\pi}{2}Q_{3}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
Q_{1}\\
Q_{2}\\
Q_{3}
\end{array}\right)\exp\left(-i\frac{\pi}{2}Q_{3}\right)
\]

\end_inset

可以得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
B & =\bra{0}\left[Q_{2},\Phi_{1}\right]\ket{0}\\
