\begin_layout Subsection
抵消项的产生
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
正规化，比如之前章节提到的维数正规化，是一种系统地把圈积分中的发散和有限贡献分开的方法。我们现在简要地讨论一下重整化（renormalization），也就是，
如何把发散吸收到 Lagrangian 的参数中。更一般地说，重整化就是用物理可观测量表示 Lagrangian 中的参数的过程，而独立于发散。
 为了简化，我们考虑一个玩具模型：两个带质量标量场自由度
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}=\frac{1}{2}\left(\partial_{\mu}\phi_{B}\partial^{\mu}\phi_{B}-M_{B}^{2}\phi_{B}^{2}\right)+\frac{1}{2}\left(\partial_{\mu}\varphi_{B}\partial^{\mu}\varphi_{B}-m_{B}^{2}\varphi_{B}^{2}\right)-\frac{\lambda_{B}}{4}\phi_{B}^{2}\varphi_{B}^{2}
\]

\end_inset

其中下标
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

表示这是裸参量。（bare parameters）。通过把裸场和裸参数表示成重整化的量，可以产生抵消项，用来吸收所有圈积分中出现的发散。我们首先引入场
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

的重整化
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi_{B}=\sqrt{Z_{\phi}}\phi,\quad\varphi_{B}=\sqrt{Z_{\varphi}}\varphi
\]

\end_inset

and then rewrite the field renormalization constants 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{Z_{\phi}}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{Z_{\varphi}}$
\end_inset

 as well as the remaining bare quantities in terms of renormalized parameters:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
Z_{\phi} & =1+\delta Z_{\phi}\left(M,m,\lambda,v\right)\\
Z_{\varphi} & =1+\delta Z_{\varphi}\left(M,m,\lambda,v\right)\\
M_{B}^{2} & =M^{2}\left(v\right)+\delta M^{2}\left(M,m,\lambda,v\right)\\
m_{B}^{2} & =m^{2}\left(v\right)+\delta m^{2}\left(M,m,\lambda,v\right)\\
\lambda_{B} & =\lambda\left(v\right)+\delta\lambda\left(M,m,\lambda,v\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

参数
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

表明了对于重整化方案的依赖。比如，我们可以要求
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

 的物理质量。选择重整化条件的自由度在重子的 ChPT 中很重要。With the subsitutions the Lagrangian 形式变成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}=\mathcal{L}_{\text{basic}}+\mathcal{L}_{\text{ct}}
\]

\end_inset

分别被称为基本和抵消项 Lagrangians
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\mathcal{L}_{\text{basic}} & =\frac{1}{2}\left(\partial_{\mu}\phi\partial^{\mu}\phi-M^{2}\phi^{2}\right)+\frac{1}{2}\left(\partial_{\mu}\varphi\partial^{\mu}\varphi-m^{2}\varphi^{2}\right)-\frac{\lambda}{4}\phi^{2}\varphi^{2}\nonumber \\
\mathcal{L}_{\text{ct}} & =\frac{1}{2}\delta Z_{\phi}\partial_{\mu}\phi\partial^{\mu}\phi-\frac{1}{2}\delta\left\{ M^{2}\right\} \phi^{2}+\frac{1}{2}\delta Z_{\varphi}\partial_{\mu}\varphi\partial^{\mu}\varphi-\frac{1}{2}\delta\left\{ m^{2}\right\} \varphi^{2}-\frac{\delta\left\{ \lambda\right\} }{4}\phi^{2}\varphi^{2}\label{eq:3.117}
\end{align}

\end_inset

其中引入了缩写
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\delta\left\{ M^{2}\right\}  & =\delta Z_{\phi}M^{2}+Z_{\phi}\delta M^{2},\\
\delta\left\{ m^{2}\right\}  & =\delta Z_{\varphi}m^{2}+Z_{\varphi}\delta m^{2},\\
\delta\left\{ \lambda\right\}  & =\delta\lambda Z_{\phi}Z_{\varphi}+\lambda\left(\delta Z_{\phi}+\delta Z_{\varphi}+\delta Z_{\phi}\delta Z_{\varphi}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

将
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.117"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

中的抵消项 Lagrangian 按照重整化的耦合常数展开，会产生无穷级数。通过适当的调节展开系数，每一项负责剪除掉圈图的发散。在下文中，我们所说的重整化的图，
指的是不仅计算了基本 Lagrangian 的贡献，还加上了抵消项 Lagrangian 的贡献。
\end_layout

