\begin_layout Standard
这些观察导致了有效 Wess-Zumino-Witten （WZW）作用量。鉴于普通的 Ward identities 与生成泛函在定域的外场变换下的
 
\emph on
invariance
\emph default
 有关（see 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:1.4.1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:1.4.4"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

）。在重整化微扰理论中首次得到的反常 Ward identities，给出了生成泛函特定形式的 
\emph on
variation
\emph default
。Wess and Zumino 推导了 anomalous Ward identities 满足的一致性或完备性关系，并清晰地构建了一个包含赝标量八重态的泛函
，满足 anomalous Ward identities。特别的，Wess and Zumino 强调说，their interaction
 Lagrangian cannot be obtained as part of a chirally invariant Lagrangian。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Witten 提出，at the Lagrangian level，给最低阶运动方程加上一项最简单的项，打破只有偶数个 Goldstone-bosons。在没有
耦合到任何外场情形，对于无质量 Goldstone-bosons ，修改的运动方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\partial_{\mu}\left(\frac{F_{0}^{2}}{2}U\partial^{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right)+\lambda\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}U\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger};U\partial_{\nu}U^{\dagger};U\partial_{\rho}U^{\dagger};U\partial_{\sigma}U^{\dagger}=0\label{eq:3.146}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

是一个纯虚数常数 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{0123}=1$
\end_inset

。在
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.146"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

替换
\begin_inset Formula $U\leftrightarrow U^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

（
\begin_inset Formula $\phi\to-\phi$
\end_inset

），然后从左边乘上
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

，从右边乘上
\begin_inset Formula $U^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

，我们可以验证，两项的符号变化相反。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\partial_{\mu}\left(U\partial^{\mu}U^{\dagger}\right) & \to U\partial_{\mu}\left(U^{\dagger}\partial^{\mu}U\right);U^{\dagger}=-\partial_{\mu}U;U^{\dagger}\partial^{\mu}U;U^{\dagger}-UU^{\dagger}\partial^{\mu}U;\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}\\
 & =\partial_{\mu}U;\partial^{\mu}U^{\dagger};UU^{\dagger}-\partial^{\mu}U;\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}=\partial_{\mu}U;\partial^{\mu}U^{\dagger}+U\partial^{\mu}\partial_{\mu}U^{\dagger}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

回忆起，拉氏量里一个 even（odd）的项导致运动方程中一个 even (odd)的项。为了写出一个对应于
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.146"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的作用量，我们需要拓展
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

的定义到一个假想的五维，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U\left(y\right)=\exp\left(i\alpha\frac{\phi\left(x\right)}{F_{0}}\right),\quad y^{i}=\left(x^{\mu},\alpha\right),i=0,\cdots,4,0\le\alpha\le1
\]

\end_inset

where Minkowski 空间定义在五维空间的表面
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=1$
\end_inset

。让我们引用 Wess–Zumino-Witten (WZW) 有效作用量的结果，在没有外场的情况下（用下标
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

表示）：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
S_{\text{WZW}}^{0}=-\frac{i}{240\pi^{2}}\int_{0}^{1}\dif\alpha\int\dif^{4}x\varepsilon^{ijklm}\tr\left(\mathcal{U}_{Li}\mathcal{U}_{Lj}\mathcal{U}_{Lk}\mathcal{U}_{Ll}\mathcal{U}_{Lm}\right)\label{eq:3.148}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中指标
\begin_inset Formula $i,\cdots,m$
\end_inset

从
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $y_{4}=y^{4}=\alpha$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{ijklm}$
\end_inset

是完全反对称张量，with 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{01234}=-\varepsilon^{01234}=1$
\end_inset

， and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{U}_{Li}\equiv U^{\dagger}\frac{\partial U}{\partial y^{i}}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\mathcal{U}_{L\mu} & =U^{\dagger}\left(y\right)U\left(y\right)i\alpha\frac{\partial_{\mu}\phi\left(x\right)}{F_{0}}=i\alpha\frac{\partial_{\mu}\phi\left(x\right)}{F_{0}},\quad\mu\in\left\{ 0,1,2,3\right\} \\
\mathcal{U}_{L4} & =U^{\dagger}\left(y\right)U\left(y\right)i\frac{\phi\left(x\right)}{F_{0}}=i\frac{\phi\left(x\right)}{F_{0}}\\
{\color{blue}\mathcal{U}_{Li}} & {\color{blue}=\frac{i}{F_{0}}\partial_{i}\left(\alpha\phi\left(x\right)\right),\quad\mu\in\left\{ 0,1,2,3,4\right\} \text{ 总的来说，可以写成这样}}
\end{align*}

